# Web Conventions

## Component Patterns

- Functional components with default exports for pages
- shadcn/ui primitives in `components/ui/` — use these before adding new dependencies
- Layout components in `components/layout/` (sidebar, app shell with `<Outlet />`)
- Icons from `lucide-react`

## Data Fetching

- All API calls go through `lib/api.ts` — typed `request<T>()` wrapper over fetch
- Use React Query (`@tanstack/react-query`) for server state
- Default stale time is 30s, retry 1 (configured in `App.tsx`)
- Add new API types and functions to `lib/api.ts`, not inline in components

## Routing

- React Router v7 with `BrowserRouter`
- Routes nested inside `<AppShell />` layout route
- Pages live in `pages/` — one file per route

## Styling

- Tailwind CSS v4 via `@tailwindcss/vite` plugin (not PostCSS)
- Use `cn()` from `lib/utils.ts` for conditional class merging (clsx + tailwind-merge)
- Dark mode supported via shadcn theme

## Imports

- Use `@/` path alias for all imports from `src/` (e.g., `@/components/ui/button`)
- Keep third-party imports above local imports
